            <h2 id="sec_updates">What's New</h2>
            <hr>
            <ul>
                <li>2015/11/27 Code of CNN-VLM was uploaded.</li>
                <li>2015/11/12 Our new paper <a href="http://arxiv.org/pdf/1511.02872v1" target="_blank">"Visual Language Modeling on CNN Image Representations"</a> (CNN-VLM) was uploaded on arXiv.</li>
                <li>2015/07/25 Our work was reported on <a href="http://www.technologyreview.com/view/537786/is-this-the-first-computational-imagination/" target="_blank">MIT Technology Review</a>.</li>
                <li>2015/06/05 Codes for our recent paper on arXiv were uploaded.</li>
                <li>2015/05/23 Longer version of CVPR 2014 paper was uploaded on arXiv.</li>
                <li>2015/04/15 Supplementary materials of CVPR 2014 paper was uploaded.</li>
                <li>2014/11/12 MATLAB code of CVPR 2014 paper was uploaded.</li>
                <li>2014/10/28 Slides and poster of MIRU 2014 talk were uploaded.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 id="sec_about">About Me</h2>
            <hr>
            <p>I'm currentry a research engineer at Sony Corporation.</p>

